---
// ValorPropuesto.astro
---

<section id="por-que-domus" class="relative py-24 bg-surface bg-noise border-y border-border overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background elements -->
  <div class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-accent/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-gold/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="text-accent font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest block mb-3">La Diferencia Domus</span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-cream mb-4">
        ¿Por qué Domus Pizzería?
      </h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-16 bg-accent mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="font-sans text-cream-muted text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        No hacemos pizza rápida. Hacemos pizza de verdad, respetando los tiempos del fermento natural y el calor ancestral de la leña.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3-Column Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      
      <!-- Card 1: Horno de Barro -->
      <div class="group bg-bg/50 border border-border p-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/40 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- SVG Icon: Horno de Barro (Fireplace/Oven) -->
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent mb-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0 1 12 21 8.25 8.25 0 0 1 6.038 7.047 8.287 8.287 0 0 0 9 9.601a8.983 8.983 0 0 1 3.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 0 0 3 2.48Z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 .495-7.467 5.99 5.99 0 0 0-1.925 3.546 5.974 5.974 0 0 1-2.133-1A3.75 3.75 0 0 0 12 18Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-cream mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-accent">
          Horno de Barro
        </h3>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-cream-muted text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Cada pizza cocida en horno de barro artesanal a 450°C. La corteza que no encontrarás en ningún otro lugar de Requinoa.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Masa Fermentada 48h -->
      <div class="group bg-bg/50 border border-border p-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/40 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- SVG Icon: Wheat/Harvest (Masa) -->
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent mb-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v18M12 3C9.5 5.5 8 9.5 8 13.5c0 3 1.5 5.5 4 7.5M12 3c2.5 2.5 4 6.5 4 10.5 0 3-1.5 5.5-4 7.5M8.5 7.5c2-1 3.5-3 3.5-3M15.5 7.5c-2-1-3.5-3-3.5-3M8 11.5c2-1.5 4-2.5 4-2.5M16 11.5c-2-1.5-4-2.5-4-2.5M8 15.5c2-1 4-1.5 4-1.5M16 15.5c-2-1-4-1.5-4-1.5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-cream mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-accent">
          Masa Fermentada 48h
        </h3>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-cream-muted text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Nuestra masa descansa dos días completos en frío lento. Más digestible, más alvéolos, más sabor, más carácter. No hay atajos en Domus.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Ingredientes Italianos -->
      <div class="group bg-bg/50 border border-border p-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/40 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <!-- SVG Icon: Tomato/Basil (Ingredientes) -->
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-accent mb-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8.25v-1.5m0 1.5c-1.355 0-2.697.056-4.024.166C6.845 8.51 6 9.473 6 10.608v2.513c0 3.28 2.378 6.07 5.568 6.575a2.22 2.22 0 0 0 1.864 0C16.622 19.19 19 16.4 19 13.12v-2.512c0-1.135-.845-2.098-1.976-2.226A42.115 42.115 0 0 0 12 8.25Z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v3.75m0 0a3.75 3.75 0 1 0 0 7.5 3.75 3.75 0 0 0 0-7.5Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-cream mb-3 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-accent">
          Ingredientes Italianos
        </h3>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-cream-muted text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Tomate Mutti San Marzano importado de Italia, Mozzarella Fior di Latte fresca, albahaca recién cortada. Lo mejor de dos mundos o nada.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
